<div class="en">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 380" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="350" y="24" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Why Conviction Grows Stronger, Not Weaker, Under Disconfirmation</text>
    <text x="350" y="44" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">The same dissonance-resolution pattern in both bulls and bears</text>

    <rect x="20" y="58" width="310" height="86" rx="8" fill="#1a1a1d" stroke="#3f3f46"/>
    <text x="175" y="80" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Disconfirmation — Bull (Strategy)</text>
    <text x="175" y="100" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Sep 2022: price below $30,639 cost</text>
