<div class="zh">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 380" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="350" y="24" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">為何信念在反證之下不減反增</text>
    <text x="350" y="44" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">多頭與空頭展現出相同的失調化解模式</text>

